---
title: Sesame Crusted Tofu with Steamed Rice & Ginger Greens
description: We just can't resist these crunchy sesame crusted tofu squares. Don't be afraid to season them very well before cooking - it will make all the difference when eating.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b6a8c46ae08b56288651fd5-487fe50b.jpg
